  "reference_number": "RUS2212",
  "remarks": "\nOMSKIY-103 (IMO 8889385) is involved in activity whose object or effect is to destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine or to obtain a benefit from or support the Government of Russia. Namely, OMSKIY-103 is involved in carrying military goods from a third country to a place in Russia.  \n",
